'''Pothos Fine''' was a [[Gender/Legends|male]] individual who once came into possession of the [[Nova Crystal]]. Because of this, [[Gordunga]] sent a group of thugs led by [[Falcon (person)|Falcon]] to kill him and retrieve the crystal. Though they did manage to kill Pothos a group of passengers from a ship which had just landed on [[Platform 11-33-D]] who tried to save him were instead rewarded with the crystal.

